# Worktree isolation staging directories (feat: worktree-isolation-per-worker)
# NOTE: .jclaw_worktrees is created as a SIBLING of the repo root (one level
# up) so it is never inside the git working tree.  A gitignore pattern here
# would be inert.  The directory is outside the repo and git never tracks it.
